description: My Airport Info provides you with status and delays at MAJOR US AIRPORTS. Tell it the airport code and it responds with, Delay, Weather, Wind and local time information
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask my airport info for PDX
Alexa, ask my airport info about P. D. X.
Alexa, ask my airport info for delays at P. D. X.
name: My Airport Info
shortDescription: My Airport Info provides you with status and delays at Major US airports.
